                I create interactive things with code. I am learning how to do
                it great.
              </p>

              <div class="button button--primary">
                <a href="/about/">more about me...</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>
      <main>
        {{ content | safe }}
      </main>

      {% include 'partials/footer.njk' %}
    </div>
    <script src="/src/script.js"></script>
    <script src="/src/fslightbox.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
